{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "dra:genesis.10",
    "translationId": "dra",
    "bookSlug": "genesis",
    "chapterNumber": 10,
    "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10",
    "summary": "Source text for Genesis 10 in Douay-Rheims Bible (Challoner)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.1",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:1",
      "text": "These are the generations of the sons of Noe: Sem, Cham, and Japheth: and unto them sons were born after the flood.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.2",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:2",
      "text": "The sons of Japheth: Gomer, and Magog, and Madai, and Javan, and Thubal, and Mosoch, and Thiras.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.3",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:3",
      "text": "And the sons of Gomer: Ascenez and Riphath and Thogorma.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.4",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:4",
      "text": "And the sons of Javan: Elisa and Tharsis, Cetthim and Dodanim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.5",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:5",
      "text": "By these were divided the islands of the Gentiles in their lands, every one according to his tongue and their families in their nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.6",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:6",
      "text": "And the Sons of Cham: Chus, and Mesram, and Phuth, and Chanaan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.7",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:7",
      "text": "And the sons of Chus: Saba, and Hevila, and Sabatha, and Regma, and Sabatacha. The sons of Regma: Saba, and Dadan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.8",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:8",
      "text": "Now Chus begot Nemrod: he began to be mighty on the earth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.9",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:9",
      "text": "And he was a stout hunter before the Lord. Hence came a proverb: Even as Nemrod the stout hunter before the Lord.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.10",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:10",
      "text": "And the beginning of his kingdom was Babylon, and Arach, and Achad, and Chalanne in the land of Sennaar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.11",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:11",
      "text": "Out of that land came forth Assur, and built Ninive, and the streets of the city, and Chale.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.12",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:12",
      "text": "Resen also between Ninive and Chale: this is the great city.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.13",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:13",
      "text": "And Mesraim begot Ludim, and Anamim and Laabim, Nephthuim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.14",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:14",
      "text": "And Phetrusim, and Chasluim; of whom came forth the Philistines, and the Capthorim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.15",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:15",
      "text": "And Chanaan begot Sidon his firstborn, the Hethite,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.16",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:16",
      "text": "And the Jebusite, and the Amorrhite, and the Gergesite.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.17",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:17",
      "text": "The Hevite and Aracite: the Sinite,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.18",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:18",
      "text": "And the Aradian, the Samarite, and the Hamathite: and afterwards the families of the Chanaanites were spread abroad.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.19",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:19",
      "text": "And the limits of Chanaan were from Sidon as one comes to Gerara even to Gaza, until thou enter Sodom and Gomorrha, and Adama, and Seboim even to Lesa.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.20",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:20",
      "text": "These are the children of Cham in their kindreds and tongues, and generations, and lands, and nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.21",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:21",
      "text": "Of Sem also the father of all the children of Heber, the elder brother of Japheth, sons were born.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.22",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:22",
      "text": "The sons of Sem: Elam and Assur, and Arphaxad, and Lud, and Aram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.23",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:23",
      "text": "The sons of Aram: Us, and Hull, and Gether; and Mes.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.24",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:24",
      "text": "But Arphaxad begot Sale, of whom was born Heber.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.25",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:25",
      "text": "And to Heber were born two sons: the name of the one was Phaleg, because in his days was the earth divided: and his brother's name Jectan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.26",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:26",
      "text": "Which Jectan begot Elmodad, and Saleph, and Asarmoth, Jare,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.27",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:27",
      "text": "And Aduram, and Uzal, and Decla,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.28",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:28",
      "text": "And Ebal, and Abimael, Saba,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.29",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:29",
      "text": "And Ophir, and Hevila, and Jobab. All these were the sons of Jectan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.30",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:30",
      "text": "And their dwelling was from Messa as we go on as far as Sephar, a mountain in the east.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.31",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:31",
      "text": "These are the children of Sem according to their kindreds and tongues, and countries in their nations.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:genesis.10.32",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "genesis",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Genesis 10:32",
      "text": "These are the families of Noe, according to their people and nations. By these were the nations divided on the earth after the flood.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
